===Verb===
'''[[go]] [[in]] [[one]] [[ear]] [[and]] [[out]] the [[other]]'''

#{{idiom}} Said of something that is heard but not attended to; (someone) failed to pay [[attention]]
#:''He told me who he saw, but it went '''in one ear and out the other'''.''

